      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-for-loop-iterating-over-a-collection&#34;&gt;1. &lt;code&gt;for&lt;/code&gt; Loop: Iterating Over a Collection&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;for&lt;/code&gt; loop is used to iterate over a sequence (like a list, tuple, or string) and execute a block of code for each item in the sequence.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
